{
  "id": "adv_main_02_07_05",
  "title": "東京編2章10話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "……反対票は星見プロだけ\n最初から、負け戦は決まっていた訳ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The only opposing vote was Hoshimi Productions…\nI suppose we were doomed from the start.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。事務所の中には、弱みを握られている所も\nあったんだろう。渋々って顔ではあったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. And I’m sure some of the agencies there\nwere coerced. I saw a lot of nervous faces.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "でも、なんで星見プロも会議に呼ばれたのかな\n仕組まれた負け戦だったんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But why was Hoshimi Productions even invited to the meeting?\nShe designed it to be rigged‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "最初から姫野さんのやり方に反対するって分かってて\nあえて呼んだってことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Himeno-san knew from the start that you’d oppose her methods‚\nand yet she still invited you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "たぶん、無視出来なかったんだと思う\nグランプリのダブル優勝の実績があるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She probably couldn’t afford to ignore us.\nWe are the agency that had a double-win in the Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "今は実力派のリズノワだって所属している\n大手事務所ではないにせよ、存在感はあるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And we’ve got the talented LizNoir signed with us now.\nEven though we’re not a big agency‚ we definitely have presence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "それで、{user}さん\n星見プロは、これからどうするんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ {user}-san‚\nwhat is Hoshimi Productions’s next move?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 50.6666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 50.6666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 50.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 50.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "社長A",
      "speakerNameEn": "President",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ところで今回の祭典、優勝したグループや事務所には",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Regarding this new festival‚ what will the winning group",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "社長A",
      "speakerNameEn": "President",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どのような褒賞を用意する予定なのでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and agency be rewarded?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 61.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "グループへの褒賞は、大規模な単独ライブ開催の確約",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The winning group will be guaranteed a large-scale solo concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そして、事務所やその代表には――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And their agency and its president",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "I.E.A.の、第一期理事長のポストを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "will be awarded one term as chairman of the IEA.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "用意しております",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That is what we’ve planned.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 73.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "理事長のポスト……ってことは、ここに集まっている\n事務所をまとめ上げる、事実上のトップですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The position of chairman… Doesn’t that mean\nyou’d be virtually in charge of all the agencies here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 83
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……そうか、それこそが……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… That’s why she’s doing this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 87.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さんの目的――\nううん、陰謀の正体だったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s Himeno-san’s motive…\nNo‚ her “conspiracy.” That’s what it really is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どういうことですの？\nもう少し分かりやすく教えてくださいませんこと！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what are you talking about?\nCouldn’t you explain it in simpler terms?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 100.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "つまり、姫野さんは最初から、協会の理事長に就任して\nアイドル業界を牛耳るつもりでいたってことよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In other words‚ Himeno-san’s plan all along was to be made chairman\nof the association so she could wrap the idol industry around her fingers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "協会の発足と、理事長就任が約束された祭典を開催する\nけどそれに当たって、強力な説得力と理由が必要だった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So she founded the association and started a festival that would determine its chairman.\nBut to make this happen‚ she needed a persuasive and valid reason.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "朝倉さんの逮捕の一件は、この陰謀のきっかけに\nうまく利用されたようなものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Asakura-san’s arrest helped set her conspiracy into motion.\nShe made good use of that scandal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さんに仕組まれた可能性もあるわ\n朝倉さんのそばにいた彼女ならチャンスはあったはず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s a possibility she orchestrated everything.\nBeing close to Asakura-san‚ she had many opportunities to make it happen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "霧子がプレタポルテに移ったのも合点がいくね\nあそこにはⅢXが在籍してるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It also adds up to why she transferred to Pret-A-Porter.\nBecause they’ve got IIIX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ⅢX……それって\nBIG4の一角、ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX… You mean\none of the pillars of the BIG4‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ、スリクスって呼ばれてる\nさらにトリエルまで抱き込んだとなると……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. IIIX.\nAnd now that they’ve got TRINITYAiLE in their grasp‚ too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "自分が必ず勝つための、最強の布陣……\nよく出来てる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An army that will guarantee her a victory…\nShe’s very thorough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "感心してる場合じゃありませんわ！\nこれから、どうするんですの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now’s not the time to be enamored by her!\nWhat are we going to do about this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さんがどうして業界を牛耳りたいのか\nその理由は分からない……でも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As for the reason why Himeno-san wants to control the idol industry‚\nthat remains unclear. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "君達アイドルが輝くための場所が\n誰かの考え一つで支配されていい訳がない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Agencies should be places where idols like you can shine.\nThey should never be under a single person’s control.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まして姫野さんのやり方じゃ、アイドルもファンも\n本当に笑えない。だから……俺は戦うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Himeno-san has her way‚ neither the idols nor the fans\nwill be truly happy. That’s why… I’m going to fight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
