    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "でも姫野さんの独裁を防ぐには、出場して\n彼女の息のかかったグループに勝たなくちゃいけない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But to thwart Himeno-san’s monopoly‚ we’ll need to participate\nand defeat the groups she has a hand in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ここにいるみんなの協力が、不可欠なんだ\nもちろん無理強いはしない……けど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll need the help of each and every one of you here.\nOf course‚ I won’t force you to join… but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です、分かってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay. We understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "その祭典、出場させて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please let us enter that festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "今更、水くさいことは言いっこなしですよ\n私達が目指しているのは、トップアイドルなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After everything we’ve been through‚ you shouldn’t keep us at a distance.\nOur dream is to become top idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "でも陰謀なんてない、誰もが平等に輝ける世界でなきゃ\nトップに立つ意味なんてありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But not by deception. This industry has to be a place where everyone has equal opportunities to shine.\nOtherwise‚ there’s no meaning in standing at the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirは……言うまでもないわね\n出場して、トリエルにも、スリクスにも勝つわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As for LizNoir… I don’t even have to say it.\nWe’ll enter the festival and defeat both TRINITYAiLE and IIIX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、お客さんが目の前にいて、歌うことができる\nファンに楽しんでもらえる、絶好の機会なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ we’ll get to stand in front of an audience and sing!\nIt’s a perfect opportunity to make our fans happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "なら、断る理由なんて、ないじゃないですか\nだって私達――アイドルなんですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So there’s no reason for us to refuse.\nAfter all‚ we’re idols!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "さくら、みんな……ありがとう。姫野さんの野望を\n阻止するためにも星見プロ全員で、優勝を狙おう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura… girls… thank you. To thwart Himeno-san’s ambitions‚\nall of us here at Hoshimi Productions will work together to win!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.53333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.1666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 265.6666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "私が半分気絶している間に、そんな熱い展開が……\nくう！　私、燃えてきましたよ～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To think that such a touching development transpired while I was half unconscious…\nOhhh! I’m so fired up now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.46666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "さっきまで燃え尽きてたのに、凄いですね！\n燃えカスも残らなくなっちゃいそうな勢いです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After you just burned yourself out? Wow‚ that’s amazing!\nYou’re burning so hard you might not even leave any ash behind!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.1333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
