      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "いいから、こころも大会概要をちゃんと確認して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cut it out‚ Kokoro. And check over the event summary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 282.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "分かってますってば～\nちゃんと読みますよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aw‚ come on‚ I get it.\nI promise I’ll read it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 288.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "今回の祭典、NEXT VENUSグランプリと違って\n参加するための条件はないんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unlike the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix‚\nthis festival has no prerequisites to enter‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 294.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。新人からトップランカーまでそろい踏みになる\nBIG4の一角、スリクスも参加するだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. Everyone‚ from newcomers to veterans‚ will compete together.\nEven IIIX‚ one of the BIG4‚ will likely compete.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.76666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
