      "text": "そこにトリエルも出場するんですよね、きっと\n……凄いイベントになりそうだなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I’m sure TRINITYAiLE will also compete.\nWow‚ it’s going to be quite the event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
