      "text": "でもこれ、下手したら一、二回戦目で\n同じ事務所同士の潰し合いになりそうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But with this format‚ one misstep‚ and in the second round‚\nwe might wind up competing against groups from our own agency.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 316.3666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、その可能性もあるわね\nくじ運次第だけど、出来れば避けたいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. That is a possibility.\nI guess it’s up to the lottery‚ but I’d like to avoid it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 323.1333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_05-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "……あれあれ？\nでも、ここに何か書いてありますよ？　えっと～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s this?\nThere’s something written about it here. Let’s see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 327.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
