      "text": "トーナメントの公平性を期すために、各参加事務所には\nそれぞれシード権を用意しています……らしいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the interest of fairness in the tournament‚ seeded groups\nwill be allowed for each agency… That’s what it says.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 336.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
